            "hadith_number_english": "30",
            "hadith_english": "Narrated Aisha, Ummul Mu'minin:\r\n\r\nWhen the Prophet ﷺ came out of the privy, he used to say: \"Grant me Thy forgiveness.\"",
            "translation_urdu": "اے اللہ! میں تیری بخشش چاہتا ہوں",
            "hadith_book_urdu": "سنن ابی داؤد",
