            "hadith_book_english": "Sunan Abi Dawood",
            "hadith_number_english": "101",
            "hadith_english": "Narrated AbuHurayrah:\r\n\r\nThe Messenger of Allah ﷺ said: The prayer of a person who does not perform ablution is not valid, and the ablution of a person who does not mention the name of Allah (in the beginning) is not valid.",
