               "hadith_english": "Ibn 'Abbas said:\r\n\r\nWe used to know that Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) had finished his prayer when we heard the takbir (Allah-O-Akbar).",
               "translation_urdu": "ﷲ سبسے بڈا ہے",
