            "hadith_number_english": "1858",
            "hadith_english": "Narrated Umm Kulthum:\r\nFrom 'Aishah that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said: \"When one of you eats food, then let him say: 'Bismillah.' If he forgets in the beginning, then let him say: 'Bismillah Fi Awwalihi Wa Akhirih (In the Name of Allah in its beginning and its end.)\"",
            "translation_urdu": "اللہ کے نام کے ساتھ اس کے شروع اور اس کے آخر میں",
